# ==============================================================================

# Location in File:
# - Add this definition to the arbitration properties section
# - It should appear between P70.18 and P70.20
# - Around line with other P70.* property definitions

# Prerequisites:
# - gmn:E31_3_Arbitration_Agreement class must be defined
# - cidoc:P70_documents must be imported from CIDOC-CRM namespace
# - cidoc:P14_carried_out_by must be imported from CIDOC-CRM namespace
# - cidoc:E39_Actor must be imported from CIDOC-CRM namespace

